      bearCase: "The bear case highlights the substantial risks associated with AI-driven finance. AI agents, if flawed or misused, could lead to rapid and significant capital losses. The current limitations of AI, coupled with regulatory uncertainty and the proliferation of speculative, low-value \'AI-crypto\' products, create an environment ripe for investor disillusionment and market instability. High-profile failures of AI trading systems or exposure of scams could severely damage confidence in the sector.",
