      probabilityWeightedOutlook: "The most probable outlook is a gradual, institutionally-led expansion of the crypto market, with a strong emphasis on real-world applications and regulatory compliance. The probability of another highly speculative, rapid-growth bull run is moderate, while the likelihood of continued regulatory pressure and enforcement is high. Overall, a weighted outlook suggests moderate-to-strong long-term growth, but with increased scrutiny and less volatility.",
